import { Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter, Box, Center, Button, Slider, SliderTrack, SliderFilledTrack, SliderThumb } from '@chakra-ui/react'

export default function App() {
    const duracion = 90

    return (
        <Box position="relative"  p={30}>
            <Center>
                <Card w="100vw" h="20vh" borderRadius="35px" >
                    <CardBody position="relative">
                        <Slider w="70vw" min={0} max={duracion} colorScheme='' defaultValue={0}>
                            <SliderTrack>
                                <SliderFilledTrack />
                            </SliderTrack>
                            <SliderThumb />
                        </Slider>
                    </CardBody>
                    <CardFooter>
                        <Button colorScheme="blue">Sign up</Button>
                    </CardFooter>
                </Card>
            </Center>
        </Box>
    );
}
